---
title: Corn, Shrimp & Green Pepper Chowder  with Old Bay Toast
description: We couldn’t be prouda of this chowda! This creamy soup has all the veggies worth boasting about, like corn, green pepper, and tender russet potatoes. Cream cheese and melty cheddar are swirled in for extra richness, then, it’s all dolloped with sour cream and garnished with scallions. On the side, there’s toasted baguette slathered with an Old Bay butter so you can sop up every last drop.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/63cff6bb3f882100da0551cd-580ddb7b.jpg
